{"tid":555160,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳展鵬大馬搞fans meeting　門票$1200超越天團BIGBANG級數","createTime":"2018-02-09T07:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T19:14:01.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e52bb68061cca32fdae951bf3e05ece398273bc1","tid":555160,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T07:45:56.000Z","msg":"近年有不少藝人都到外地登台，接近農曆新年當然是他們搵真銀的好日子。早前馬明受訪時，都話情人節同新年都接咗 job，可想而知嗰酬勞係有幾咁好。貴為視帝嘅陳展鵬今日就係Instagram上載海報，透露自己將於年初二會到吉隆坡開fans meeting，最貴門票一張要約$1200港幣，個票價仲超越了歌神張學友同韓國天團BIGBANG同樣在馬來西亞的演唱會和見面會！！<br />\n有參加過fans meeting嘅粉絲都知買得最貴門票，見面會之後都可以同偶像近距離接觸。根據陳展鵬今次po出的海報中，原來粉絲無論是買最貴價還是最便宜的門票 ，都有機會同佢有近距離接觸。不少粉絲見到都紛紛留言話一定會買飛親睹偶像，仲話會買埋佢設計嘅眼鏡到場！<br />\n以歌神張學友演唱會和BIGBANG 三子的見面會為例，最貴價門票分別只需馬幣￥688（即港幣$1376）及￥550（即港幣$1100）。你以為學友同BIGBANG嘅門票就係最貴？咁你就太年輕了！根據網上資料，天后王菲在馬來西亞舉行的演唱會係史上最貴嘅，因為一張要馬幣￥1080（即港幣$2160）。所以今次陳展鵬門票只要￥588（即港幣$1176），值唔值就見仁見智，但相信粉絲們為了見偶像，呢啲錢又點會介意花呢？！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/158283/thumbnail/cf94d8f00671a2d730f41fbe0283987a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F158283%2Fthumbnail%2Fcf94d8f00671a2d730f41fbe0283987a.jpg&h=d75d5103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/158283/%E9%99%B3%E5%B1%95%E9%B5%AC%E5%A4%A7%E9%A6%AC%E6%90%9Efans-meeting-%E9%96%80%E7%A5%A8-1200%E8%B6%85%E8%B6%8A%E5%A4%A9%E5%9C%98BIGBANG%E7%B4%9A%E6%95%B8#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F158283%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25B1%2595%25E9%25B5%25AC%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%2590%259Efans-meeting-%25E9%2596%2580%25E7%25A5%25A8-1200%25E8%25B6%2585%25E8%25B6%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%259C%2598BIGBANG%25E7%25B4%259A%25E6%2595%25B8%23%26gid%3D1%26pid%3D1&d=LPJKfcuqLuhsPVaPwbkrtb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=6686f724\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/158283/%E9%99%B3%E5%B1%95%E9%B5%AC%E5%A4%A7%E9%A6%AC%E6%90%9Efans-meeting-%E9%96%80%E7%A5%A8-1200%E8%B6%85%E8%B6%8A%E5%A4%A9%E5%9C%98BIGBANG%E7%B4%9A%E6%95%B8#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=1</a>"},{"pid":"fb2a4d0a401a8e417dee8ac1931e885f89e2dde1","tid":555160,"uid":131259,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T08:36:46.000Z","msg":"有冇行天橋環節先?<br />\n有既都值依個價"},{"pid":"75befbe955829cc01bc7b6d3db4ab56028c69181","tid":555160,"uid":30510,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T08:44:46.000Z","msg":"朱sir ho ball"},{"pid":"ec795dca9a82869afd88d07f684015df8cb625e9","tid":555160,"uid":23021,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T08:59:26.000Z","msg":"不少粉絲見到都紛紛留言話一定會買飛親睹偶像，仲話會買埋佢設計嘅眼鏡到場！<br />\n<br />\n好想睇成場都戴果副野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98657a1c10550bc638da8367d51ade39e396a8c","tid":555160,"uid":19287,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T09:07:11.000Z","msg":"見親佢個樣總覺得佢係一隻屎忽鬼"},{"pid":"b135b08484753a6c2f415bf23ab3a864fd9fc523","tid":555160,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T09:16:29.000Z","msg":"其實大馬黎講，係咪都係港星紅過韓星？"},{"pid":"3def999413c78704804dbfbb0c2037c0e6d3aaea","tid":555160,"uid":82917,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T13:05:38.000Z","msg":"用千二蚊去睇亞視鵬，笑撚到我仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啲呀姑級鵬友可唔可以包養我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05cf4184cb12d46bf4ebc6f259acc0167d1cee2f","tid":555160,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ec795dca9a82869afd88d07f684015df8cb625e9","tid":555160,"uid":23021,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T08:59:26.000Z","msg":"不少粉絲見到都紛紛留言話一定會買飛親睹偶像，仲話會買埋佢設計嘅眼鏡到場！<br />\n<br />\n好想睇成場都戴果副野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"re